        <br>
        <p class="col-bold-text">100+</p>
        <p class="col-subtext-grid2">applications on the BC Gov<br />DevOps platform</p>
        <a href="~/Views/Home/DevOpsPlatform.cshtml" class="btn btn-default community-btn" style="width:150px;">Learn More</a>
    </div>
    <div class="col22">
        <img class="col22-img" src="~/img/bcdevx-home-image.jpg" alt="bcdevExchange-img">
    </div>
</div>

@*Third part*@
<div class="container grid-cont3">
    <div class="col31">
        <img class="col31-img" src="~/img/bcdevx-home-image.jpg" alt="bcdevExchange-img">
    </div>
    <div class="col32">
        <p class="col-bold-text">Trying to be Agile but still not sure how?</p>
        <p class="col-subtext">With the Lab Residency at the Exchange Lab, we help teams accelerate their Agile Journey </p>
        <br>
        <br>
        <p class="col-bold-text">10+</p>
        <p class="col-subtext-grid2">teams from different BC Gov Ministries<br/>have graduated from the Exchange Lab </p>
